      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s been so well-taken care of over the years. It\u2019s in really nice shape and still drives like a dream! It\u2019s the perfect balance of comfort and dependability, just waiting for its next owner to take the wheel. Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
