    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a Double-VANOS system refresh to ensure precise cam timing. The chassis retains its signature poise thanks to updated trailing arm bushings and a functional variable M differential lock. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains tight and the throttle response is exceptionally crisp. A true enthusiast's specimen ready for the B-roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
